          ( shudders, sobs )

702
00:42:07,358 --> 00:42:09,959
( door shuts )

703
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,430
            - Here.
            - Thanks.

704
00:42:18,569 --> 00:42:22,138
     - So, where's the baby
         going to sleep?
