00:45:41,271 --> 00:45:43,272
          She even posted
          a picture of the test.

756
00:45:43,373 --> 00:45:45,708
                 Hey, I was
                 calling, and...

757
00:45:45,776 --> 00:45:49,612
    ( whispering ) I was calling
    and texting you all night.
    The results came back.

758
00:45:49,680 --> 00:45:52,849
